<br>
Dwarfs - they tend to be heavy drinkers, full of pride (sometimes too much), quick to temper, and can be the life of a good party.  That could be good or bad depending on the mood of said dwarf.<br>
<br>
Gnomes - I don't know much about Gnomes other than they are a tricky sort.  Check your boot straps when standing from a meal when a Gnome is around, Or ye might find yourself with a face full of dirt and a Gnome giggling in the background.<br>
<br>
Frogloks - Were recently freed from slavery by Marr.  They are humbled and proud of thier God Marr. They readly fight under Marr and all that they percieve as evil in the lands of Norrath.  So basicly a Dwarf without the ale and temper. etc etc.<br>
